comments: Dudley (BKN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Fox (SAC) and absorbs the contact.
Bjelica (SAC) legally contests Russell's (BKN) shot attempt at the rim.
MOB shows Hollis-Jefferson (BKN) blocks the shot attempt before the ball makes contact with the backboard.
RAR and RLS show Dudley (BKN) make contact to the head of Fox (SAC) and affect his driving shot attempt.
Dudley (BKN) establishes himself in a legal picking position by firming up and absorbing the contact from Hield (SAC).
LAR shows Barnes (SAC) jumps legally alongside Russell (BKN) with his left arm collapsed against his body and his right arm contesting the shot at the rim.
Dudley (BKN) obtains a legal guarding position when he beats Fox (SAC) to the spot and absorbs the contact to his chest.
As Fox (SAC) is about to switch on to Dudley (BKN) after the pick, both players hook each other's arms but immediately disengage.
MOB and RLB show Bagley III (SAC) make contact with Russell's (BKN) arm and affect his driving shot attempt.
Dudley (BKN) does not establish himself in a legal guarding position by beating Fox (SAC) to the spot and the contact affects Fox's SQBR.
Fox (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Russell (BKN) during the start of the drive.
Hield (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Russell (BKN).
Barnes (SAC) clamps Hollis-Jefferson's (BKN) arm and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
LLS shows Hollis-Jefferson (BKN) legally moves alongside of Bagley III (SAC) and Bagley III initiates the contact.
Kurucs (BKN) makes clean contact with the ball and knocks it away from Bagley III (SAC).
RAR shows Hollis-Jefferson (BKN) and Bagley III (SAC) make incidental contact with each other as they attempt to retrieve the loose ball.
Bagley III (SAC) is out of bounds while in contact with the ball.
LLS shows Bagley III (SAC) makes marginal contact with Hollis-Jefferson's (BKN) arm as he gathers the ball.  Hollis-Jefferson jumps into Bagley III and initiates the body contact.
Dudley (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the shot attempt by Hield (SAC).
